{"tid":1818540,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想同朋友去旅行可以點做","createTime":"2020-01-10T03:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T21:29:45.000Z","uid":113784,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c6b9691465ee457a9de109b7541ce592f17f8d","tid":1818540,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我有一班朋友A 一直我哋幾個好想一齊去旅行<br />\n但我唔想<br />\n<br />\n事緣係我覺得同佢哋唔係去旅行嘅伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去過一次台灣 第一日已經鬧交<br />\n雖然之後幾日玩得ok冇<br />\n但我覺得自己夾唔到佢哋嘅style<br />\n<br />\n事隔咗好耐 之前聖誕住過一晚酒店過夜<br />\n我都唔係好ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更莫講話去幾日旅行<br />\n譬如好大聲傾計/玩 次次都俾人投訴、好夜訓、玩on9嘢 等等<br />\n<br />\n相反我同其他朋友夾得到 就會成日同佢哋去旅行<br />\n朋友group A見到又會話 唉又同人去旅行喇 我哋呢<br />\n<br />\n但我自己同佢哋做frd係冇問題 只係唔想一齊去旅行<br />\n<br />\n請問唔傷害友誼底下可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（冇錢 / 冇假 唔可以做藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"3edb96c71077c77b753f63fbdf5cee64b9b241e6","tid":1818540,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:54:54.000Z","msg":"一直好想我哋幾個*"},{"pid":"c2aa46699b84170c76708001bd395bec7d6c334f","tid":1818540,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c1616f45f83c67a133aa4be4c07cf119ac1714e","tid":1818540,"uid":252320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"你都已經講左有咩問題,點解唔直接同佢地講<br />\n你搵理由推都無用架,下次你再同其他人去旅行佢地又咪無限loop"},{"pid":"dd509fc2fdbc585ccc0b29592a7a34d5d61eb3ec","tid":1818540,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b8a6147a1f59a8cbc5457e657245cff936bdfa","tid":1818540,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c1616f45f83c67a133aa4be4c07cf119ac1714